Generic single-database configuration for Alembic.

This directory contains Alembic migration scripts for the AI Safety Course Platform.

## Usage

After setting DATABASE_URL in .env:

    # Mark current database as at baseline
    alembic stamp 001

    # Create a new migration
    alembic revision --autogenerate -m "description"

    # Apply all pending migrations
    alembic upgrade head

    # Rollback one migration
    alembic downgrade -1

    # Show current revision
    alembic current

    # Show migration history
    alembic history
